alerts.description:
There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 65-80 km/h; Wind direction: south then south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 90 km/h

There is a slight risk of icy surfaces (Level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 400 m

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: ~ -1 °C

There is a risk of snowfall (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Precipitation amounts: 7-20 cm; in windward areas: < 30 cm

There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Precipitation amounts: 1-7 cm
